\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-05-at-22.25.08-910x1024.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-12565\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-05-at-22.25.08-910x1024.jpeg 910w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-05-at-22.25.08-267x300.jpeg 267w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-05-at-22.25.08-768x864.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-05-at-22.25.08-400x450.jpeg 400w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-05-at-22.25.08.jpeg 914w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 910px) 100vw, 910px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bb17942 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"bb17942\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3174683 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"3174683\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-28f94c2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"28f94c2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Itinerary Overview<\/h3><p><b>Day 1: Marrakech to Boumalne Dades<\/b><\/p><p>Departure in the morning from Marrakech.<\/p><p>Pass through the Tizi n&#8217;Tichka Pass and High Atlas Mountains.<\/p><p>Visit the historic Ait Benhaddou Kasbah and explore Ouarzazate.<\/p><p>Continue through Skoura and the Valley of Roses to reach Boumalne Dades.<\/p><p>Overnight stay: Boumalne Dades in a charming guesthouse.<\/p><p><b>Day 2: Boumalne Dades to Merzouga<\/b><\/p><p>Breakfast and departure toward Todra Gorge for a short hike.<\/p><p>Drive through the scenic valleys and villages to Merzouga.<\/p><p><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text );\">Enjoy a camel trek into the Erg Chebbi dunes.<\/span><\/p><p>Witness the sunset and spend the night in a desert camp under the stars.<\/p><p><b>Day 3: Merzouga to Marrakech (via Nkob)<\/b><\/p><p>Early morning sunrise over the dunes.<\/p><p>Breakfast and departure via Rissani, Alnif, and Nkob.<\/p><p>Pass through the Draa Valley and Agdez before returning to Marrakech.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>2 Day Merzouga Desert Adventure Discover the magic of the Merzouga Desert on this 2-day adventure, where golden dunes, serene camel rides, and the timeless beauty of Berber culture await under the shimmering desert stars. Itinerary Overview Day 1: Marrakech to Boumalne Dades Departure in the morning from Marrakech. Pass through the Tizi n&#8217;Tichka Pass [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0,"parent":11314,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-12573","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/12573","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],